reviews.review_text:
great sounding aud so i have a buddy that has the july 78 box set in hi-res and was trying to figure out which shows i wanted to keep since the whole thing is like 25GB.  was surprised at how good this sounded.  don't hesitate to give it a listen!  

just checked out the hi-res from the box and it sounds fantastic but i kind of miss hearing the audience cheer..  ended up keeping this show and 7/8
